    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for devices or tools used for compressing, flattening, giving a denser consistency to, holding, or shaping an object or substance by exerting pressure, whether mechanical or not.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
